data.description: A beautiful historic home in Lander! This property offers so much to the discerning buyer. Walking distance to local schools & just minutes from downtown, this property also boast a large and private yard with mature trees and a seasonal stream. Inside, historic details abound in the living room & dining room. Generously sized bedrooms for any size household. The accessory dwelling unit, large covered patio and great location make this house a must see. Call Jonathan Rensch  @ 307-438-5056 for your private showing!
